" application."
msgstr ""
"**client_secret**: Der Client Secret, den Sie beim Registrieren Ihrer "
"Anwendung erhalten haben."

#: ../../source/using_api/oauth2.rst:104
msgid ""
"**grant_type**: The type of the authorization grant you were awarded. This "
